RT @NYDailyNews: Malik Basit, the rapper and founding member of the hip-hop group The Roots, has died at age 47.

Malik B. was remembered by Roots members Questlove and Black Thought for his devotion to Islam and his innovation as one of the "most gifted MCs of all time.”

text:
Tigers have been seen in western Thailand for the first time in four years, an encouraging sign for the future of the animals, wildlife officials say. 

Poaching and deforestation have wiped out tigers and their habitats worldwide.
